#. message: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:230
msgid ""
"Sixteen years into her rule, Asheviere turned her attention to the Wood "
"Elves living in the great forest southwest of Wesnoth, whom she despised. "
"Orcish mercenaries were hired and dispatched to bring about their ruin."
msgstr ""
"Шеснаест година по доласку на власт, Ашевира скрену своју пажњу ка шумским "
"вилењацима, које је презирала, што живеше у великој шуми југозападно од "
"Веснота. Она унајми и отпосла орковске плаћенике да вилењацима смрсе конце."

#. message: description=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:234
msgid ""
"Master Delfador! Look, there are orcs coming from all directions! What shall "
"we do?"
msgstr ""
"Учитељу Делфадоре! Гледај, то орци избијају са свих страна! Шта нам је "
"чинити?"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:238
msgid "There are too many to fight, far too many. We must escape!"
msgstr "Превише их је да бисмо се борили, превише. Морамо се склонити!"

#. message: description=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:242
msgid "But to where? This is the only home we have! What about the elves?"
msgstr "Али куда? Ово је једини дом који имамо! Шта ће бити са вилењацима?"

#. message: description=Galdrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:246
msgid ""
"We will fight them, but you must escape, Konrad. It is imperative that you "
"escape!"
msgstr ""
"Ми ћемо се борити, али ти Конраде мораш отићи. Суштински је важно да "
"избегнеш!"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:250
msgid ""
"We will go north. Perhaps we can reach the Isle of Alduin. If we can make it "
"there, surely we will be safe. Konrad, we must recruit some elves to help "
"us, and then you must make it to the sign post in the north-west. I will "
"protect you!"
msgstr ""

#. message: description=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:254
msgid "Very well, let us hurry!"
msgstr "У реду, пожуримо онда!"

#. message: description=Urug-Telfar
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Attack the elves, my grunts, and take their villages. Let us claim this land "
"for the Queen!"
msgstr ""
"Удрите на вилењаке, грокташи моји, и узмите њихова села. Покоримо ову земљу "
"за Краљицу!"

#. message: description=Knafa-Tan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:267
msgid ""
"Remember, it is rumored that the filthy mage and one that he protects are in "
"these parts. They are the ones we want!"
msgstr ""
"Запамтите, прича се да прљави маг и његов штићеник пребивају у овим "
"пределима. Они морају бити наши!"

#. message: description=Knafa-Tan
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:273
msgid "Ha ha! We will rip the filthy elves to pieces!"
msgstr "Ха, ха! Покидаћемо прљаве вилењаке на комадиће!"

#. message: description=Galdrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:278
msgid "Let them come. We will fight them with all we have!"
msgstr "Нека дођу. Борићемо се свиме што имамо!"

#. message: description=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:282
msgid "Be careful, Konrad! Guard him well, Delfador!"
msgstr "Буди опрезан, Конраде! Добро га чувај, Делфадоре!"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:286
msgid "And so it has begun!"
msgstr "И тако, отпоче..."

#. message: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:305
msgid "OK, we have made it this far! But where do we go next?"
msgstr "У реду, стигосмо до овде! Али куда ћемо даље?"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:309
msgid ""
"We must travel north, and try to make it to the Isle of Alduin. Hopefully we "
"will find refuge there."
msgstr ""

#. message: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:313
msgid ""
"Of course you are right, Delfador. But what will become of the elves here?"
msgstr "Наравно да си у праву, Делфадоре. Али шта ће постати од вилењака овде?"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:317
msgid ""
"The elves will fight. They may even prevail. But I fear things do not bode "
"well for them. Let us not speak of it now. Onward!"
msgstr ""
"Вилењаци ће се борити. Можда чак и одоле нападу. Али се бојим да им се мрко "
"пише. Нећемо сада о томе. Напред!"

#. message: description=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:321
msgid "Good luck, Konrad! Don't worry about us, we will fight as best we can!"
msgstr "Са срећом, Конраде! Не брини за нас, борићемо се најбоље што знамо!"

#. message: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:336
msgid "I... I don't think I can make it anymore."
msgstr "Мислим... Мислим да не могу даље."

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:340
msgid "Prince... you must keep fighting! Nooooooo!"
msgstr "Принче... мораш се још борити! Неееее!"

#. message: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:344
msgid "It is over. I am doomed..."
msgstr "Готово је. Пропао сам..."

#. message: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:358
msgid "I have... have failed in my duty to protect the prince! I am defeated."
msgstr "Не... не изврших своју дужност да заштитим принца! Поражен сам."

#. message: description=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:362
msgid "Don't die, Delfador! Please, you have to stay alive!"
msgstr "Не умири, Делфадоре! Преклињем те, мораш остати жив!"

#. message: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:366
msgid "Ugh"
msgstr "Уххх"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:377
msgid ""
"Oh, no! We have run out of time, they have arrived with reinforcements..."
msgstr "О, не! Време нам је истекло, стигоше са појачањима..."

#. message: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:396
msgid "Die, Villain, die!"
msgstr "Умри, зликовче, умри!"

#. message: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:407
msgid "Only the foolish oppose me!"
msgstr "Само се будале мени супротстављају!"

#. message: description=Galdrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:418
msgid "I am Galdrad. You will have to fight me to get any further!"
msgstr "Ја сам Галдрад. Мораћеш преко мене ако желиш да крочиш ма корак даље!"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:429
msgid "Only a fool would dare to attack me!"
msgstr "Само би се будала усудила да ме нападне!"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:440
msgid "I am Delfador the Great. Prepare to die!"
msgstr "Ја сам Делфадор Велики. Помири се са судбином!"

#. message: description=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:452
msgid "Let me through, you rogue!"
msgstr "Пропусти ме, ниткове!"

#. message: description=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:467
msgid "Oh no! They are destroying our home!"
msgstr "О не! Они разарају наш дом!"

#. message: description=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/01_The_Elves_Besieged.cfg:471
msgid "There can be no looking back. We must go quickly!"
msgstr "Не смемо се освртати. Морамо брзо напред!"

